## Summary

Bootstrap Atmos Pro CI/CD integration for `ex`. Generated by the `atmos-pro`
skill from a fresh repo analysis — no manual edits.

**What this adds**

- `stacks/mixins/atmos-pro.yaml` — single import point, disables Spacelift, declares `settings.pro`
- `stacks/catalog/aws/iam-role/{defaults,gha-tf}.yaml` — OIDC-trusted plan + apply IAM roles
- `components/terraform/aws/iam-role/component.yaml` — vendor manifest
- `profiles/github-plan/atmos.yaml`, `profiles/github-apply/atmos.yaml` — per-account identities
- `.github/workflows/atmos-pro.yaml`, `atmos-pro-list-instances.yaml`,
  `atmos-terraform-plan.yaml`, `atmos-terraform-apply.yaml`
- Additive edit to `stacks/catalog/tfstate-backend/defaults.yaml` (wildcard trust)
- `docs/atmos-pro.md` with the full rollout procedure

**Accounts enabled (6):**

- `core-root` (`111111111111`) — root account, apply pinned to plan role
- `core-identity` (`222222222222`)
- `core-audit` (`333333333333`)
- `plat-dev` (`444444444444`)
- `plat-staging` (`555555555555`)
- `plat-prod` (`666666666666`)

## Rollout checklist

- [ ] Set `ATMOS_PRO_WORKSPACE_ID` and `ATMOS_VERSION` as GitHub repo **variables** (not secrets)
- [ ] Verify `github-oidc-provider` is deployed to every target account
- [ ] Deploy plan IAM roles to every account
- [ ] Deploy apply IAM roles to every non-root account
- [ ] Deploy the tfstate-backend trust update
- [ ] Run the `Test AWS OIDC` workflow to verify end-to-end
- [ ] Merge this PR
- [ ] Open a trivial test PR to exercise the dispatch flow

## Security notes

- Plan role has `ReadOnlyAccess` but can read Terraform state via the tfstate role. Anyone who
  can trigger a workflow can read state.
- Apply role is scoped to `main` branch only. Automation cannot apply from a PR branch.
- Root account is pinned to the plan role in the apply profile — automation cannot apply to root.


## Spacelift migration

Spacelift was previously enabled for this org. The generated mixin disables it
(`settings.spacelift.workspace_enabled: false`). Existing Spacelift state is not migrated.
Stacks that were overridden: see `docs/atmos-pro.md` for the list.

